  "detailed_description": "<strong>WWII Tanks: Forgotten Battles<br>Choose your side USA/Great Britain, Axis or USSR!<br>Participate in the biggest historical tank battles of World War II!<br>Go through the entire war on different tanks, feel the horror of war on your skin!<br><br>Game Features:<br>       <ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Beautiful graphics</li></ul>       <ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Realistic tanks of the WWII</li></ul>       <ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Historical maps and battles</li></ul>       <ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Possibility to choose tanks</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Game mode:</h2>       <ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Single Missions</li></ul>       <ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Three Campaigns (USA/UK, AXIS and URSS) </li></ul><br>Wide selection of famous WWII tanks:<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Germany:</h2>       <ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Tiger 1</li></ul>       <ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Panzer-IV</li></ul>       <ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Sdkfz251</li></ul>       <ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Mörser Karl</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >USSR:</h2>      <ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>T-34/76</li></ul>      <ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>T-34/85</li></ul>      <ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>KV-I</li></ul>      <ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>KV-II</li></ul>      <ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>BT-7</li></ul>      <ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>T-35</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Japan:</h2>     <ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Type 89</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Finland:</h2>  <br>      <ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>BT-42</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >United Kingdom:</h2>    <ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Cromwell</li></ul>    <ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Sherman Firefly</li></ul>and many more.</strong>",
